name: Earthnicity Mix
description:
Earthnicity Mix

A weirdly semi complicated mix

The MAIN merge mix is listed at Epic Mix's new update, and the only extra thing included in any of this is: 25D Lora, and @bombasticmori 's moth mix: https://civitai.com/models/50041?modelVersionId=73614

Their mix recipe is on THEIR model card.

The commmercial lisc downstream on this is different than Epic mix.

The 2.5D version includes a different version of Moth Mix compared to the Anime style of this version.

While conceptually it's SIMILAR to Epic Mix because it has EPIC MIX + Kilkenny 2.5D in it?
LOL, we didn't wanna clog up Epic mix with different downstream perms.

Plus uh, the name's a nod to Jacksepticeye, because our best friends whole branding is "earthnicity" - and According to them, "Sean can't even say Ethnicity" or it rather he said it wrong once, and it came out as "EARTHNICITY" XD

We're starting a new initiative with our models: Fighting for accessibility in Art for not just everyone but specifically mental and physical disability spaces. AI art isn't JUST a tool, it's a new way of expression for those unable to do so before.

PLEASE NOTE: IMAGES MAY NOT SHARE THE SAME FILE NAME AS MODELS THAT ARE UPLOADED.

VAE: We use KF-L-Anime, but it is entirely up to you.

WE ARE PROUDLY SPONSORED BY: https://www.piratediffusion.com/

If you got requests, or concerns, We're still looking for beta testers: JOIN THE DISCORD AND DEMAND THINGS OF US: https://discord.gg/5t2kYxt7An

Lora Request Form: https://forms.gle/NEkcMmVEjG4pBAP7A

JOIN OUR SUBREDDIT: https://www.reddit.com/r/earthndusk/

Listen to the music that we've made that goes with our art:
https://open.spotify.com/playlist/00R8x00YktB4u541imdSSf?si=b60d209385a74b38

We stream a lot of our testing on twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/duskfallcrew

Pre-Release Models, Lora Backups - Send us pizza! https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew
